Articles.Content:
I built this ship to go to dres. Its a 2 part ship first part is tug/lander combo and second is the transfer stage. I got the parts in orbit and docked so now its just sittin in orbit waitin to be tested!!!

Let me know what u think!

Edited April 21, 2014 by Billyk88
Sorry images are not working for some reason
Looks good, must have been a pain to get it in orbit in such a big chunk

Honestly the transfer section was the hardest but it actually wasnt that bad with all the new nasa parts. The tug/lander was by the easiest but dockin was a pain cause the transfer stage is so big that it took a bit of time to get in the right position to dock.
